text: Johannes Bloemen (26 May 1864 - 15 March 1939) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre backstroke at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1864 births Category:1939 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers from Amsterdam Category:Male backstroke swimmers
